        },
        "rich_text_T6wbJY": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choosing the Right Setting for Your Lifestyle and Style",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Choosing the Right Setting for Your Lifestyle and Style</h2><p>There’s no single “best” setting - it depends on how you plan to wear your jewellery.</p><p>You might prefer prong settings if you:<br/><br/>1.]Love <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/classic-engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"classic engagement ring \">classic engagement ring </a>designs<br/>2.]Want maximum sparkle<br/>3.]Want the diamond to stand out more<br/><br/>You might prefer bezel settings if you:<br/><br/>1.]Like modern and minimal jewellery<br/>2.]Want extra protection for the diamond<br/>3.]Wear jewellery every day<br/><br/>At Lucira Jewelry, our collections include both styles so customers can choose what feels right for them.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "choosing-the",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8qLjXa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Many People Actually Choose Both Settings for Different Jewellery Pieces",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Many People Actually Choose Both Settings for Different Jewellery Pieces</h2><p>Interestingly, many customers don’t choose just one setting. They use both in their jewellery collection.</p><p>For example:</p><p>1.] A prong-set solitaire ring for special occasions<br/>2.] A bezel-set tennis bracelet for everyday wear<br/><br/>This way you get the sparkle of prong settings and the durability of bezel designs.</p>",
            "custom_id": "many-people",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_MjDG7a": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lucira Approach to Diamond Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Lucira Approach to Diamond Jewellery</h2><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, every piece is designed with both beauty and practicality in mind. Our collections feature modern designs crafted with IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, offering brilliance along with responsible sourcing.</p><p>Whether it’s a classic six-prong solitaire stud or a refined bezel-set tennis bracelet, each Lucira piece is created to be worn comfortably and loved for years.</p><p>Our goal is simple: jewellery that feels modern, elegant, and easy to wear every day.</p>",
            "custom_id": "the-lucira",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Thoughts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Thoughts</h2><p>Both bezel and prong settings have their own charm.</p><p>Prong settings are perfect if you want the diamond to sparkle as much as possible. Bezel settings are great if you prefer a smooth, secure design for everyday use.</p><p>In the end, the best setting is the one that fits your style and how you like to wear your jewellery.</p><p>And with thoughtfully designed pieces from Lucira, you can enjoy diamonds that combine elegance, comfort, and lasting brilliance.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "final-thoughts",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
